247	/// Tiny FSC-name decoder. Covers the codes a stub on a fresh AddrSpace
248	/// would actually hit. The full table (ARM ARM D13.2.40) has ~30 codes;
249	/// we just want boot-log triage to be tractable. Slice 3.2's real PF
250	/// handler will branch on FSC and replace this with structured handling.
251	fn fsc_name(fsc: u64) -> &'static str {
252	    match fsc {
253	        0x04 => "translation fault, L0",
254	        0x05 => "translation fault, L1",
255	        0x06 => "translation fault, L2",
256	        0x07 => "translation fault, L3",
257	        0x09 => "access flag fault, L1",
258	        0x0A => "access flag fault, L2",
